/* Content
----------------------------------------------- */
body {
font: normal normal 12px Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif;
color: #000000;
background: #cfe7d1 url(//themes.googleusercontent.com/image?id=1x_TqXo6-7t6y2ZiuOyQ2Bk6Zod9CTtyKYtRui0IeQJe6hVlJcQiXYG2xQGkxKvl6iZMJ) repeat fixed top center /* Credit: gaffera (http://www.istockphoto.com/googleimages.php?id=4072573&amp;platform=blogger) */;
padding: 0 0 0 0;
background-attachment: scroll;
}
html body .content-outer {
min-width: 0;
max-width: 100%;
width: 100%;
}
h2 {
font-size: 22px;
}
a:link {
text-decoration:none;
color: #249fa3;
}
a:visited {
text-decoration:none;
color: #7c93a1;
}
a:hover {
text-decoration:underline;
color: #5dc2c0;
}
.body-fauxcolumn-outer .fauxcolumn-inner {
background: transparent url(//www.blogblog.com/1kt/simple/body_gradient_tile_light.png) repeat scroll top left;
_background-image: none;
}
.body-fauxcolumn-outer .cap-top {
position: absolute;
z-index: 1;
height: 400px;
width: 100%;
background: #cfe7d1 url(//themes.googleusercontent.com/image?id=1x_TqXo6-7t6y2ZiuOyQ2Bk6Zod9CTtyKYtRui0IeQJe6hVlJcQiXYG2xQGkxKvl6iZMJ) repeat fixed top center /* Credit: gaffera (http://www.istockphoto.com/googleimages.php?id=4072573&amp;platform=blogger) */;
background-attachment: scroll;
}
.body-fauxcolumn-outer .cap-top .cap-left {
width: 100%;
background: transparent url(//www.blogblog.com/1kt/simple/gradients_light.png) repeat-x scroll top left;
_background-image: none;
}
.content-outer {
-moz-box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .15);
-webkit-box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .15);
-goog-ms-box-shadow: 0 0 0 #333333;
box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .15);
margin-bottom: 1px;
}
.content-inner {
padding: 0 0;
}
.main-outer, .footer-outer {
background-color: #ffffff;
}
/* Header
----------------------------------------------- */
.header-outer {
background: transparent none repeat-x scroll 0 -400px;
_background-image: none;
}
.Header h1 {
font: normal bold 70px Georgia, Utopia, 'Palatino Linotype', Palatino, serif;
color: #000000;
text-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .2);
}
.Header h1 a {
color: #000000;
}
.Header .description {
font-size: 200%;
color: #000000;
}
.header-inner .Header .titlewrapper {
padding: 22px 30px;
}
.header-inner .Header .descriptionwrapper {
padding: 0 30px;
}
/* Tabs
----------------------------------------------- */
.tabs-inner .section:first-child {
border-top: 0 solid #dddddd;
}
.tabs-inner .section:first-child ul {
margin-top: -0;
border-top: 0 solid #dddddd;
border-left: 0 solid #dddddd;
border-right: 0 solid #dddddd;
}
.tabs-inner .widget ul {
background: transparent none repeat-x scroll 0 -800px;
_background-image: none;
border-bottom: 0 solid #dddddd;
margin-top: 0;
margin-left: -0;
margin-right: -0;
}
.tabs-inner .widget li a {
display: inline-block;
padding: .6em 1em;
font: normal normal 20px Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif;
color: #00818b;
border-left: 0 solid #ffffff;
border-right: 0 solid #dddddd;
}
.tabs-inner .widget li:first-child a {
border-left: none;
}
.tabs-inner .widget li.selected a, .tabs-inner .widget li a:hover {
color: #444444;
background-color: transparent;
text-decoration: none;
}
/* Columns
----------------------------------------------- */
.main-outer {
border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
}
.fauxcolumn-left-outer .fauxcolumn-inner {
border-right: 1px solid #dddddd;
}
.fauxcolumn-right-outer .fauxcolumn-inner {
border-left: 1px solid #dddddd;
}
/* Headings
----------------------------------------------- */
div.widget &gt; h2,
div.widget h2.title {
margin: 0 0 1em 0;
font: normal bold 11px Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif;
color: #000000;
}
/* Widgets
----------------------------------------------- */
.widget .zippy {
color: #999999;
text-shadow: 2px 2px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
}
.widget .popular-posts ul {
list-style: none;
}
/* Posts
----------------------------------------------- */
h2.date-header {
font: normal bold 11px Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, FreeSans, sans-serif;
}
.date-header span {
background-color: transparent;
color: #000000;
padding: inherit;
letter-spacing: inherit;
margin: inherit;
}
.main-inner {
padding-top: 30px;
padding-bottom: 30px;
}
.main-inner .column-center-inner {
padding: 0 15px;
}
.main-inner .column-center-inner .section {
margin: 0 15px;
}
.post {
margin: 0 0 25px 0;
}
h3.post-title, .comments h4 {
font: normal normal 22px Chewy;
margin: .75em 0 0;
}
.post-body {
font-size: 110%;
line-height: 1.4;
position: relative;
}
.post-body img, .post-body .tr-caption-container, .Profile img, .Image img,
.BlogList .item-thumbnail img {
padding: 2px;
background: #ffffff;
border: 1px solid #eeeeee;
-moz-box-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
-webkit-box-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
box-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
}
.post-body img, .post-body .tr-caption-container {
padding: 5px;
}
.post-body .tr-caption-container {
color: #000000;
}
.post-body .tr-caption-container img {
padding: 0;
background: transparent;
border: none;
-moz-box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
-webkit-box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
box-shadow: 0 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
}
.post-header {
margin: 0 0 1.5em;
line-height: 1.6;
font-size: 90%;
}
.post-footer {
margin: 20px -2px 0;
padding: 5px 10px;
color: #666666;
background-color: #f9f9f9;
border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
line-height: 1.6;
font-size: 90%;
}
#comments .comment-author {
padding-top: 1.5em;
border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
background-position: 0 1.5em;
}
#comments .comment-author:first-child {
padding-top: 0;
border-top: none;
}
.avatar-image-container {
margin: .2em 0 0;
}
#comments .avatar-image-container img {
border: 1px solid #eeeeee;
}
/* Comments
----------------------------------------------- */
.comments .comments-content .icon.blog-author {
background-repeat: no-repeat;
background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);
}
.comments .comments-content .loadmore a {
border-top: 1px solid #999999;
border-bottom: 1px solid #999999;
}
.comments .comment-thread.inline-thread {
background-color: #f9f9f9;
}
.comments .continue {
border-top: 2px solid #999999;
}
/* Accents
---------------------------------------------- */
.section-columns td.columns-cell {
border-left: 1px solid #dddddd;
}
.blog-pager {
background: transparent none no-repeat scroll top center;
}
.blog-pager-older-link, .home-link,
.blog-pager-newer-link {
background-color: #ffffff;
padding: 5px;
}
.footer-outer {
border-top: 0 dashed #bbbbbb;
}
/* Mobile
----------------------------------------------- */
body.mobile  {
background-size: auto;
}
.mobile .body-fauxcolumn-outer {
background: transparent none repeat scroll top left;
}
.mobile .body-fauxcolumn-outer .cap-top {
background-size: 100% auto;
}
.mobile .content-outer {
-webkit-box-shadow: 0 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, .15);
box-shadow: 0 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, .15);
}
body.mobile .AdSense {
margin: 0 -0;
}
.mobile .tabs-inner .widget ul {
margin-left: 0;
margin-right: 0;
}
.mobile .post {
margin: 0;
}
.mobile .main-inner .column-center-inner .section {
margin: 0;
}
.mobile .date-header span {
padding: 0.1em 10px;
margin: 0 -10px;
}
.mobile h3.post-title {

                  <div class="post-outer">
                   <div class="post hentry" itemprop="blogPost" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
                    <meta content="data:image/jpeg;base64," itemprop="image_url"/>

                    </a>
                    <h3 class="post-title entry-title" itemprop="name">
                     Start A Business With New Business Loans
                    </h3>
                    <div class="post-header">
                     <div class="post-header-line-1">
                     </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-body entry-content" id="post-body-278679926441028707" itemprop="description articleBody">
                     <div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;" trbidi="on">
                      <div style="text-align: justify;">
                       <a href="http://www.newbusinessloans.org.uk/applynow.php" target="_blank">
                        <img alt="http://www.newbusinessloans.org.uk/applynow.php" height="163" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," width="320"/>
                       </a>
                      </div>
                      <div style="text-align: justify;">
                       Do you intend to start a new business in the near future? Have you listed the essential requirements for the start-up of your new business venture? If yes, then the most primary requirement that you need for your dream business is the capital.
                       <br/>
                       <br/>
                       So, if you do not possess adequate funds it is impossible for you to commence a new business. Since the money is needed to establish your office, pay your employees and so on, you need to have enough working capital.
                       <br/>
                       <br/>
                       When you start a new business, you can find that there are several uncountable expenses. In order to meet these expenses have you planned to raise cash? If not, then without thinking twice, you can go for new business loans.
                       <br/>
                       <br/>
                       You might be wondering as to how much money you will be able to fetch from these
                       <a href="http://www.newbusinessloans.org.uk/" target="_blank">
                        <b>
                         New Business Loans
                        </b>
                       </a>
                       . Keep aside your worries! The amount of cash released to you is not fixed but, determined on the basis of your needs and repaying capacity.
                       <br/>
                       <br/>
                       Lenders will give enough time to pay back the borrowed cash with matching repayment tenure to suit your budget. The amount that you derive from these loans can be freely utilized for any purpose you wish.
                       <br/>
                       <br/>
                       You need to follow a simple and easy online application process. Searching the web for lenders offering you these loans will help you to select the best lender providing you these loans on affordable rates and terms.
                       <br/>
                       <br/>
                       These are unsecured loans and hence, lenders do not ask you to arrange for any security against the loan sum approved. There is no credit review done for you by the lenders. You need not be worried about your negative profile as it will be ignored by the lender.
                       <br/>
                       <br/>
                       Just submit the online form with all the details without any paperwork. The form is available online at the lenders website. With this arrangement, lender will approve your loan and wire the amount to your account. Now, you can start your dream business without any hurdles.
                       <br/>
                       <br/>
                       Opting for
                       <a href="http://www.newbusinessloans.org.uk/bad_credit_new_business_loans.html" target="_blank">
                        <b>
                         Bad Credit New Business Loans
                        </b>
                       </a>
                       will enable you to manage adequate working capital required for starting your new business venture. You can get sufficient cash by applying through an online mode, which is easy and simple.
                       <br/>
                      </div>
